    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Groups of all copies printed at the same time. A single impression in publishing includes all of the copies of a book produced during one printing, or print-run, or an additional press-run made without revision of text.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
